{"hash":"1fc9582b9254edacc102e172f82d7e80e2d43044","data":{"doc":{"title":"Cobertura Jacoco","path":"/plugins/jacoco/","date":"20. September 2025","content":"<p>Este plugin integra JaCoCo con Wakamiti para generar cobertura de código a partir de la ejecución de casos de prueba.</p>\n<p>Qué hace:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Se conecta al agente JaCoCo en tiempo de ejecución y vuelca (dump) los datos de ejecución (.exec) al finalizar\ncada caso de prueba.</li>\n<li>Opcionalmente, genera reportes por caso de prueba en XML y/o CSV si se configuran las rutas de salida.</li>\n<li>Al finalizar la ejecución, puede generar un informe HTML agregado de cobertura si se configura su ruta de salida.</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong></p>\n<p>El agente JaCoCo debe estar iniciado en modo <code class=\"language-text\">tcpserver</code> y escuchando en el <code class=\"language-text\">host</code> y <code class=\"language-text\">port</code> configurados. De lo\ncontrario no será posible volcar la cobertura. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<ul id=\"toc\">\n<li><a href=\"#instalaci%C3%B3n\">Instalación</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#configuraci%C3%B3n\">Configuración</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocodumphost\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.host</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocodumpport\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.port</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocodumpoutput\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.output</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocodumpretries\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.retries</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreportxml\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.xml</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreportcsv\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.csv</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreporthtml\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.html</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreportclasses\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.classes</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreportsources\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.sources</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreporttabwith\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.tabwith</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jacocoreportname\"><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.name</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"instalación\"><a href=\"#instalaci%C3%B3n\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Instalación</h2>\n<p>Incluye el módulo en la sección correspondiente.</p>\n<div id=\"coord\" class=\"remark-code-tabs\"><label for=\"coord#0\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#0 name=\"coord\" checked/> yaml\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\">es.iti.wakamiti:jacoco-wakamiti-plugin:1.0.0</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">es.iti.wakamiti:jacoco-wakamiti-plugin:1.0.0</pre></div></div><label for=\"coord#2\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#2 name=\"coord\" /> maven\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\">&lt;dependency>\n  &lt;groupId>es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId>\n  &lt;artifactId>jacoco-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId>\n  &lt;version>1.0.0&lt;/version>\n&lt;/dependency></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n  &lt;groupId&gt;es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId&gt;\n  &lt;artifactId&gt;jacoco-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n  &lt;version&gt;1.0.0&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre></div></div></div>\n<hr class=\"remark-code-tabs-x\" rel=\"coord#maven\" />\n<h2 id=\"configuración\"><a href=\"#configuraci%C3%B3n\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Configuración</h2>\n<h3 id=\"jacocodumphost\"><a href=\"#jacocodumphost\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.host</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">localhost</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nombre de host o dirección IP del agente jacoco.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">host</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 192.168.5.6</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocodumpport\"><a href=\"#jacocodumpport\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.port</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">6300</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Puerto del agente jacoco.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">port</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1234</span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocodumpoutput\"><a href=\"#jacocodumpoutput\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.output</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">.</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ruta donde se escribirán los datos de ejecución.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> some/directory</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocodumpretries\"><a href=\"#jacocodumpretries\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.dump.retries</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">integer</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">10</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Número de reintentos.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">retries</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreportxml\"><a href=\"#jacocoreportxml\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.xml</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Directorio de salida para informes XML. Se creará un informe XML para cada caso de prueba y no se creará si no se\nespecifica este parámetro.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">xml</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> some/directory/xml</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreportcsv\"><a href=\"#jacocoreportcsv\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.csv</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Directorio de salida para informes CSV. Se creará un informe CSV para cada caso de prueba y no se creará si no se\nespecifica este parámetro.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">csv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> some/directory/csv</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreporthtml\"><a href=\"#jacocoreporthtml\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.html</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Directorio de salida para el informe HTML.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> some/directory/html</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreportclasses\"><a href=\"#jacocoreportclasses\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.classes</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code> <em>required</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ubicación de los archivos de clase Java.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">classes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> target/classes</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreportsources\"><a href=\"#jacocoreportsources\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.sources</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">path</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ubicación de los archivos fuente.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">sources</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> src/main/java</pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreporttabwith\"><a href=\"#jacocoreporttabwith\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.tabwith</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">integer</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">4</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ancho de la tabulación para las páginas de origen.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">tabwith</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jacocoreportname\"><a href=\"#jacocoreportname\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">jacoco.report.name</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code class=\"language-text\">JaCoCo Coverage Report</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nombre utilizado para este informe.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jacoco</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">report</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>    \n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Wakamiti coverage report</pre></div>\n"}},"context":{"id":"1840976926b201acb0a5abc5fd3bb34b","path":"/plugins/jacoco/","locale":"es"}}